data.description: Lovely and private waterfront home on a large landscaped lot with protected dockage.  Bring all your family to entertain by the waterside with so much patio space and an outside bar. Storage galore inside and out for every water toy.  This home is perfectly located with protected boating access for fun bayside yet easy to ocean through Adams Cut.  No matter the weather, you can play!  Ready for your family and an easy commute to the mainland.
